findings.title: Out of gas
findings.description: The functions setIncludeInReward() and getCurrentSupply() use loops to find and remove addresses from the _excluded list and evaluate total supply, respectively. If there is a long excluded addresses list, these functions may be aborted with an OUT_OF_GAS exception.

findings.title: Owner privileges (In the period when the owner is not renounced)
findings.description: The contract owner has excessive privileges to perform various actions such as withdrawing ERC20 tokens, changing fee receivers and rates, enabling/disabling swap and liquify, excluding addresses from autoliquidity, rewards, and fees.
